      see third_party/pdfium/LICENSE
  - PDFium — BSD-3-Clause (Google) and others
      see third_party/pdfium/licenses/pdfium.txt
  - Component libraries (FreeType, libpng, zlib, lcms, libjpeg-turbo, libtiff,
    libopenjpeg, ICU, Abseil, AGG 2.3, fast_float, simdutf, llvm-libc, …)
      see third_party/pdfium/licenses/

Bundled PDFium build version: see third_party/pdfium/VERSION

When redistributing binaries of PDR, include the third_party/pdfium/LICENSE and
third_party/pdfium/licenses/ files alongside pdfium.dll.
